Typically you press either the A, B or start button with your right thumb after moving an indication object (cursor) with the directional pad (left thumb) near the character graphics depicting "SAVE" or "LOAD" displayed on-screen.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=20">kyuusaku</a> — Tue Nov 03, 2009 9:52 pm</p><hr />
